---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Specialty Cleaning Services - Alpha Cleaning">
	<main>
		<h1>Specialty Cleaning Services</h1>
		<p>From carpet cleaning to window washing, we offer a range of specialty services.</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Carpet and upholstery cleaning</li>
			<li>Window washing</li>
			<li>Pressure washing</li>
			<li>Post-construction cleaning</li>
		</ul>
		<p>Our specialty services are designed to tackle those tough cleaning jobs that require extra attention and specialized equipment.</p>
		<a href="/contact" class="cta-button">Get a Quote</a>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		margin: auto;
		padding: 1rem;
		width: 800px;
		max-width: calc(100% - 2rem);
		color: white;
		font-size: 20px;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}
	h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 1em;
		color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
	}
	.cta-button {
		display: inline-block;
		background-color: rgb(var(--accent));
		color: white;
		padding: 0.5em 1em;
		border-radius: 0.25em;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: bold;
		margin-top: 1em;
	}
	.cta-button:hover {
		background-color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
	}
</style>